########################################
########################################
####### Sw-description Generator #######
########################################
########################################

--  What is it ? --
Sw-description_generator is a tool to generate automatically sw-description. 

-- How to use it ? --
Lauch it with xterm -e source scripts/swdescription_generator.sh
Configure the generator with the rights path
Fill in images and archive informations
Create sw-desctiption  

-- Keys --
To have secure update, you need to have public and private key. 
You can generate it with key_generator.sh script

